name: Spinal Twist
description: Lay on your back, arms outstretched, and twist gently.

name: Neck Tilt
description: Sit upright and gently tilt your head from side to side.

name: Shoulder Roll
description: Roll your shoulders forward and backward.

name: Hamstring Stretch
description: Stand and bend forward, reaching for your toes.

name: Quadriceps Stretch
description: Stand on one foot and pull the other foot behind you.

name: Hip Flexor Stretch
description: In a lunge position, push your hips forward.

name: Side Stretch
description: Stand tall and reach one arm over your head, bending to the side.

name: Chest Opener
description: Clasp your hands behind your back and open up your chest.

name: Wrist Stretch
description: Extend one arm and gently pull back on your fingers.

name: Ankle Circles
description: Lift one foot and rotate your ankle in circles.

name: Cat-Cow Pose
description: On all fours, arch and round your back.

name: Child's Pose
description: Kneel down and stretch arms forward on the ground.

name: Seated Forward Bend
description: Sit with legs straight and reach for your toes.

name: Butterfly Stretch
description: Sit down, bring feet together, and push knees down.

name: Tricep Stretch
description: Raise one arm overhead, bend it, and gently push on the elbow.

name: Calf Stretch
description: Step one foot back and press heel to the floor.

name: Standing Quad Stretch
description: Stand on one leg and pull the other foot towards your buttocks.

name: Cross-body Shoulder Stretch
description: Pull one arm across your body and hold it.

name: Downward Dog
description: From a plank position, push hips up and back.

name: Cobra Pose
description: Lay on your stomach and gently push up with your arms.

name: Pigeon Pose
description: From all fours, bring one knee forward and stretch.

name: Deep Lunge
description: Step one foot forward into a lunge and lean into it.

name: Bridge Pose
description: Lay on your back, bend knees, and lift hips.

name: Seated Spinal Twist
description: Sit down, cross one leg over the other and twist.

name: Standing Forward Fold
description: Stand tall and fold forward from the hips.
